<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-48-0344 </DOCNO><TEXT>There has naturally been a world-wide interest in the development of theLARCODEMS and a number of licences has been granted by British Coal.A plant is being built in Belgium incorporating the LARCODEMS, and itmay that another will be built here soon in the United States. BritishCoal is convinced of the benefits of using the LARCODEMS to the extentthat the preparation plant for a new mine at Margam in South Wales, dedicatedtotally to producing high grade coking coal for steel making, will include2 units. This plant is due to be commissioned in 1990/91 when the minecomes on-stream.</TEXT></DOC>